 They make life a lot easier with their customer friendly online shop. You will be dazzled with excellent service by very knowledgeable staff as well as the best wine bargains no one can beat. You can choose your wine, make your purchase and within a few hours to a few days you will have your wine delivered to your doorstep – depending on where you live. GETWINE has been on an amazing journey into wine -, business – and relationship building since 2005. The three Wegner brothers, Johan, Ad and Karel head up this business with each of them in a very key role to make sure GETWINE runs as smoothly as it is today. If you want to get out a bit and see what GETWINE is all about, they will welcome you with open arms to their Salt River warehouse. They are also known for their massive wine sales in major cities all over the country. Here you can see, smell and taste the wine before you buy them. GETWINE brings the convenience and knowledge to you! Visit www.getwine.co.za and place your order or visit their warehouse as it doesn’t get any more convenient. You can also reach them on 021 461 2891 or have a look at their social media pages for updates! Man en vrou op skietbaan gewond Is your money safe at Absa? PHOTOS and VIDEO: Fire destroys Little Elephant Horrific R555 accident claims lives Grond in die soeklig   • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za